Recursive-descent top-down calculator
for Question1 part f.
author: WANG Haicheng
date  : Mar 28, 2017

To compile:   

make rdcal_postfix

OR

flex rdcal_postfix.l; gcc -o rdcal_postfix lex.yy.c rdcal_postfix.c



To execute:
(1) using file pipe
./rdcal_postfix <[filepath]
(2) interactive

./rdcal_postfix  [press ENTER]
[type postfix expression]


Important note:
the calculator has a limit that the result must be in the range
2^(-32) , 2^(32)-1, otherwise it will have integer overflow error